In [2]:
# 对属性名进行标准化重命名
data.columns=['Sex','Race','Age_at_diagnosis','Marital_status_at_diagnosis','Insurance_Recode','Grade',
              'Surgery','Tumor_size','First malignant primary indicator','Survival_months',
              'Vital_status_recode','T_stage','N_stage','M_stage','Stage_Group']

# 种族属性
data['Race'].replace({'White':'W','Black':'B','Asian or Pacific Islander':'API','American Indian/Alaska Native':'AI'},inplace=True)

# 诊断时的婚姻状况
data['Marital_status_at_diagnosis'].replace({'Widowed':1,'Divorced':1,'Single (never married)':1,'Unmarried or Domestic Partner':1,'Separated':0,'Married (including common law)':0},inplace=True)

# 保险状况
data['Insurance_Recode'].replace({'Any Medicaid':1,'Insured':1,'Insured/No specifics':1,'Uninsured':2},inplace=True)

# 组织学分级
data['Grade'].replace(['Well differentiated; Grade I','Moderately differentiated; Grade II','Poorly differentiated; Grade III','Undifferentiated; anaplastic; Grade IV','Unknown'],[1,2,3,4,np.NaN],inplace=True)

# 是否有第一恶性主要指标
data['First malignant primary indicator'].replace(['Yes','No'],[1,0],inplace=True)

# 生死状态
data['Vital_status_recode'].replace(['Dead','Alive'],[1,0],inplace=True)

# 删除含有空缺值的行
data.dropna(axis=0,how='any',inplace=True)

探究手术种类对不同分期患者的生存效益影响¶

In [16]:
# Log-rank检验函数

from lifelines import KaplanMeierFitter
from lifelines.statistics import multivariate_logrank_test

def log_rank(data):

    results=multivariate_logrank_test(event_durations=data['Survival_months']/12, groups=data['Type_of_surgery'],event_observed=data['Vital_status_recode'])

    results.print_summary()
    
def log_rank_surgry(data):

    results=multivariate_logrank_test(event_durations=data['Survival_months']/12, groups=data['Surgery'],event_observed=data['Vital_status_recode'])

    results.print_summary()

# 定义对于不同分期的患者的手术选择的画图函数

def plt(data,string):
    
    kmf.fit(data['Survival_months']/12, event_observed=data['Type_of_surgery']==0,label='No surgery of primary site')

    kmf.plot_survival_function() 

    kmf.fit(data['Survival_months']/12, event_observed=data['Type_of_surgery']==1,label='Local tumor destruction')

    kmf.plot_survival_function() 

    kmf.fit(data['Survival_months']/12, event_observed=data['Type_of_surgery']==2,label='Local tumor excision')

    kmf.plot_survival_function() 

    kmf.fit(data['Survival_months']/12, event_observed=data['Type_of_surgery']==3,label='Gastrectomy(partial, subtotal, hemi-)')

    kmf.plot_survival_function()

    kmf.fit(data['Survival_months']/12, event_observed=data['Type_of_surgery']==4,label='Near-total or total gastrectomy')

    kmf.plot_survival_function()

    kmf.fit(data['Survival_months']/12, event_observed=data['Type_of_surgery']==5,label='Gastrectomy, NOS WITH removal of a portion of esophagus ')

    kmf.plot_survival_function()

    kmf.fit(data['Survival_months']/12, event_observed=data['Type_of_surgery']==6,label='Gastrectomy with a resection in continuity with the resection of other organs')

    t=kmf.plot_survival_function(figsize=[4,4])
    t.set_title(string)
    t.legend(loc='lower left', scatterpoints=1)
    t.set_xlabel('Time/Year')
    t.set_ylabel('survival Probability')
    t.legend(bbox_to_anchor=(1.08, 0), loc=3, borderaxespad=0)
